text: Shemia Patricia Fagan (born September 20, 1981) is an American lawyer and politician. She was the Oregon Secretary of State from 2021 to 2023. She was a Democratic member of the Oregon Senate from in 2019 to 2021. She also was a member of the Oregon House of Representatives from 2013 to 2017. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Lawyers from Portland, Oregon Category:Politicians from Portland, Oregon Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:State legislators of the United States
